item.title: Get a PhD
item.author: sample@gmail.com (Dimple Bhuta)
item.description: I am exploring the possibility of pursuing a PhD, most likely in Europe, with a research focus on autonomous navigation in unstructured and adverse environments. I want to achieve this goal before my 60th birthday.
